{"tid":2510443,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優慘遭灌酒性侵！精神崩潰考慮住院治療　揭惡狼是他","createTime":"2021-04-30T07:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T08:24:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf32d141697a6f1e2f407eac90faff4a7f2fed5","tid":2510443,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"29歲日本AV女優一花琴音（舊名：寶生莉莉、宝生リリー）出身於日本宮城縣，有著甜美的長相加上火辣的身材，不過一花琴音曾遭到性暴力對待導致終生不孕。日前一花琴音在推特發文，提到自己遭約會對象性侵，因此精神崩潰，生活出現障礙，已考慮要住院治療，嚇壞一票網友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/30/3133480-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F30%2F3133480-PH.jpg&h=21e2745c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本AV女優一花琴音擁有甜美長相、火辣身材。（圖／翻攝自宝生リリー推特）<br />\n<br />\n一花琴音29日在推特發文「謝謝你的閱讀」，揭露約會遭性侵的事件。由於一花琴音在首次約會時，對約會對象的印象不錯，因此本月22日又出去約會第二次，對方竟然無視她的反抗，強灌酒精並性侵得逞，讓她精神崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/30/3133478-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F30%2F3133478-PH.jpg&h=e9b50a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲一花琴音透露約會遭性侵，讓她精神崩潰。（圖／翻攝自宝生リリー推特）<br />\n<br />\n「我沒想到第二次約會就遇到這樣子的事情，我現在根本不敢接觸男人。」一花琴音不知道何時能夠克服心理障礙，重回工作崗位，且開始無意識地做出傷害自己的行為，回想仍覺得很可怕，如今她已考慮住院治療。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/30/3133483-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F30%2F3133483-PH.jpg&h=b800125d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼一花琴音曾罹患子宮頸癌，可說是命運多舛。（圖／翻攝自宝生リリー推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/30/3133481-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F30%2F3133481-PH.jpg&h=e06cab9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一花琴音過去曾遭性暴力，導致終身不孕，還因為收入極度不穩讓她數度失控，火氣一來不只把事務所抽成後的超低片酬公諸於世，2017年曾直播中吞下大量不明藥物，又表示自己罹患子宮頸癌，可說是命運多舛。"},{"pid":"c754c6bee54eb3390208b1090387b28b1687df83","tid":2510443,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:16:48.000Z","msg":"你老婆俾人性侵咗幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2179aacf24e6b469ba118322cc7cdbda892cb96","tid":2510443,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c754c6bee54eb3390208b1090387b28b1687df83","tid":2510443,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:16:48.000Z","msg":"你老婆俾人性侵咗幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"佢性侵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351896348fef926300d48776d88b442dc6a6ca5e","tid":2510443,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"醜拉"},{"pid":"5b61bf42c6e496b49c10b6f81d349d413aba193f","tid":2510443,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"呢條女正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c5ec5add5faad4ade6805fc7f518bd1a167bf5","tid":2510443,"uid":361975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"咁都甜美長相"},{"pid":"73ae2420c1d2a6148709ec7d02aece308d386572","tid":2510443,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"351896348fef926300d48776d88b442dc6a6ca5e","tid":2510443,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"醜拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"Chuu醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf77c7c8282450bfd1a8053970f809d94f21ad5","tid":2510443,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73ae2420c1d2a6148709ec7d02aece308d386572","tid":2510443,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"351896348fef926300d48776d88b442dc6a6ca5e","tid":2510443,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re